data.description:
I've made a few albums of this guy before, and almost every time I mention him, I bring up how he acts around me, and how it's the complete opposite of what people say cats are like. This is the album to prove it.

If anybody would like to see more of Griffey (the cat in the album), just say so in the comments! He's the best OC I can provide.

If you want to see his brother Tyson, then I guess that's okay too.

Request Update 1: @imsupposedtosay asked for ear hole rubs, so here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=orI8Ts3evDk

Late FP Edit: Wow, I didn't expect this much attention, not only did you guys manage to set the record of my highest scoring post on Imgur, bur somehow, someone on Imgur's staff found this, and Griffey is going up on Imgur's Facebook page! I don't know if i can communicate how astounded I am by this, but seriously, wow.

I guess at this point, Inbox me your cats? All cats that get sent in get a spot on the next album, with the owner's username credited with it.

FP Edit 2: Apparently, this has hit Most Viral 3 times now. Wow.

images.description: As you can see, he is perfectly fine if I touch his teeth. I would've grabbed a toothbrush for this, but I couldn't find his.
Messing with his claws, and the little divot in his paw. pretty much any cat will take your arm off if you try this.
This is how he prefers to be rubbed. I've seen him simply get up and walk away from people because they weren't rubbing his belly, or they weren't rubbing him fast enough.
